        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <p class="text-bone text-sm font-semibold">Setup gratuito</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">Nosotros te configuramos todo. Cero estrés.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
